snippet.title: Johnny Depp $50mil Lawsuit To Go Ahead After Heard Failed AGAIN To Get Suit Tossed
snippet.description:
So despite all Amber Heard's attempts the $50mil Defamation lawsuit is going ahead and all the information will come out, the case is set to start in April 2022 where either Johnny Depp or Amber Heard will win, this is case will also have a direct impact on Heard's countersuit for $100mil.

Source:
https://deadline.com/2021/08/johnny-depp-trial-wins-amber-heard-defamation-lawsuit-uk-libel-verdict-1234816975/
